---
/**
 * Sección "Bienvenida a GaliaBeauty" de la Home.
 */
---

<section class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-content">
      <h2>Bienvenida a GaliaBeauty</h2>
      <p>
        En Estética Galia cuidamos de ti con una selección de tratamientos
        diseñados para realzar tu belleza y bienestar: faciales, corporales,
        mirada, depilación láser y asesoramiento cosmético personalizado. Te
        escuchamos, te asesoramos y te acompañamos para encontrar el
        tratamiento perfecto para ti, porque cada piel y cada persona son únicas.
      </p>

      <div class="features-grid">
        <a href="/servicios?categoria=facial" class="feature">
          <div class="feature-image-bg">
            <img src="/images/tratamiento-facial.png" alt="Tratamiento facial" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="feature-overlay"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Tratamientos Faciales</h3>
            <p>Tecnología avanzada para el cuidado de tu piel</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/servicios?categoria=corporal" class="feature">
          <div class="feature-image-bg">
            <img src="/images/tratamiento-facial.png" alt="Tratamientos corporales" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="feature-overlay"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Tratamientos Corporales</h3>
            <p>Tratamientos para grasa localizada, celulitis y flacidez</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/servicios?categoria=depilacion" class="feature">
          <div class="feature-image-bg">
            <img src="/images/tratamiento-facial.png" alt="Depilación láser" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="feature-overlay"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Depilación Láser</h3>
            <p>Despídete del vello, da la bienvenida a la comodidad</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/servicios?categoria=mirada" class="feature">
          <div class="feature-image-bg">
            <img src="/images/tratamiento-facial.png" alt="Mirada" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="feature-overlay"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Mirada</h3>
            <p>Luce pestañas y cejas perfectas cada día</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="ovaco-badge-container">
        <p class="ovaco-badge">
          <span class="check-icon">✓</span>
          <strong>Centro Oficial OVACO</strong> – Cosmética profesional de última generación
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 1rem 0 2rem;
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    color: var(--color-logo);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .about-content h2::after {
    content: "";
    display: block;
    width: 90px;
    height: 6px;
    margin: 0.75rem auto 0;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-cream), var(--color-logo));
    box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .about-content > p {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-logo);
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto 3.5rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  /* Features grid */
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .feature {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    height: 400px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
  }

  .feature:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .feature-image-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .feature-image-bg img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature:hover .feature-image-bg img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .feature-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.1) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.6) 100%);
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .feature-content {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    padding: 2rem;
    z-index: 3;
    color: white;
  }

  .feature h3 {
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .feature p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
    text-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  /* OVACO Badge */
  .ovaco-badge-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .ovaco-badge {
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 0.9rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: calc(var(--radius-lg) + 4px);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    transition: transform var(--transition-base), box-shadow var(--transition-base);
    width: max-content;
  }

  .ovaco-badge:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .check-icon {
    background: #fdf4eb;
    color: #d4a373;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about { padding: 0.5rem 0 1.5rem; }
    .about-content h2 { font-size: 1.75rem; }
    .about-content > p { font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .feature { height: 280px; border-radius: 16px; }
    .feature h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; }
    .feature p { font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .ovaco-badge { padding: 0.6rem 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem; gap: 0.5rem; }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .feature { height: 450px; }
    .feature h3 { font-size: 1.75rem; }
  }
</style>
